title: Sean F. Kennedy and the Three Minute Fix
description:
Sean F. Kennedy and the Three Minute Fix      
     

Artist: Sean F. Kennedy and the Three Minute Fix

Source: CD 
Format: MP3/Lame 320K
Genre:  Rock and Roll
Track List:

01. Human Condition
02. Everytime
03. Trading Sanity for Amnesty
04. The Antagonist
05. Interesting Change of Events



This is the first EP from Sean F. Kennedy and the Three Minute Fix     


When a group of music students get together for beers, and the
conversation strikes a chord (ok, sorry) to the tune of...

"what happened to rock and roll?" 

...somebody chimes in with the comment

"Think you can do better?"

to which we replied...

"Yes...yes, we do"..So we did. We think...


Check them out.  Give them some love.  Indie Bands need support.  Hit them up on myspace if you like it.  Give it to everyone you know if you like it.  Request they play it on the radio and request that they come to your town.  They ROCK live.

Thank You.

Enjoy....
